rows.label: tlk4140004203_msg0001
rows.name:
That Bamibami's shaping out to be quite
the capable recruit.

rows.label: tlk4140004203_msg0002
rows.name:
Sure he throws his weight around, but
his skills are not to be sniffed at. Even
the Nopon hold him in high regard.

rows.label: tlk4140004203_msg0003
rows.name: I can see why he was hired as a spy.

rows.label: tlk4140004203_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, he's on our side now. At least,
until the Fusty Fungus underground
runs out...
